  "texts": [
    "The correlation-based clustering represented by network graphs allows for easy market visualization.",
    "On the standard methodology to build trees, for each pair i, j of assets, the distance d",
    "is computed, where ρ ij describes the correlation between log-return time-series.",
    "Having d i,j, we can compute MST or, equivalently, the Single Linkage Clustering Algorithms (SLCA) by using, for instance, Kruskal's algorithm.",
    "Such clustering analysis for portfolio optimization was explored by Tola et al. (2008)."
  ],
